text: Diaperville is a census-designated place in the town of Sanborn, Ashland County, Wisconsin, United States. Its population was 70 as of the 2010 census. Diaperville was also called Old Odanah.Tribal Members: A Surprising Diverse Group, Elizabeth Arbuckle Watindato, PH.D, Robert M.
